entries.journal_entry_description: Working for the Hutt on Naboo.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Borvo has informed you that a group of bounty hunters are tracking you down. There are probably four of them. Make sure you deal with them before seeing Borvo again.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: I've found the spot where the bounty hunters were looking for me. I need to find and kill them before they kill me.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Ha Ha Ha! I knew those bounty hunters would be no match for you! You've done well for yourself. Come back and see me, I have another job for you.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Now that I've eliminated the Bounty Hunters Borvo has something else he wants me to do.
